      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a consistent service history, though it is approaching a interval for routine fluid changes. The exterior paint retains a nice gloss, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with regular driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only slight wear visible on the driver's seat bolster. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for daily use without needing immediate major repairs.",
