      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m selling my absolute gem of a car and it is seriously stunning! I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014it's always been kept in the garage and stays sparkling clean. It looks and drives just like it\u2019s brand new, honestly! No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner so happy. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
