    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including a VANOS system overhaul, rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells, and a reinforced rear subframe. The chassis remains stiff and responsive, complemented by a perfectly dialed-in suspension with zero bushing play. Clad in original paint with a factory-fresh interior, this M3 represents the pinnacle of the analog driving era. All service records are meticulously documented, ensuring the variable M differential and Getrag 420G transmission operate with surgical precision.",
      "price": 48500.0,
